title: Scarlett Johansson & Jonathan Bailey Answer The Web's Most Searched Questions
text: Jurassic World Rebirth stars Scarlett Johansson & Jonathan Bailey visit WIRED to offer answers to their most searched for questions on Google. Is Jonathan Bailey dating Scarlett Johansson? What was Scarlett Johansson's break out role? Is Jonathan Bailey actually singing in Wicked? When did Scarlett Johansson host Saturday Night Live? What music does Jonathan Bailey listen to? Answers to these questions and more await on the WIRED Autocomplete Interview of Scarlett Johansson and Jonathan Bailey.
